WEBVTT

00:07:59.536 --> 00:08:01.176
whether they'd license their patents or not.

00:08:01.176 --> 00:08:03.380
They were forced to do so.

00:08:03.380 --> 00:08:07.302
That is something that the Medicines Patent Pool cannot do.

00:08:07.302 --> 00:08:10.654
It relies on the willingness of pharmaceutical companies

00:08:10.654 --> 00:08:14.224
to license their patents and make them available

00:08:14.224 --> 00:08:18.764
for others to use.

00:08:18.764 --> 00:08:23.929
Today, Nelson Otwoma is healthy.

00:08:23.929 --> 00:08:27.911
He has access to antiretroviral drugs.

00:08:27.911 --> 00:08:31.688
His son will soon be 14 years old.